# This is the hex map we'll test with:
# remember: +y is N, +x is NE
"""
	                     .
	                  .
	               .     .
	            .     .
	         .     .     .
	      .     .     .
	   .     .     .     .
	.     O     B     .
	   OF    O     .     C
	.     E     O     .
